Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Unemployment looms in Hollywood
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w2q4
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 29 Jun 1980
As the recession begins to bite, even Hollywood is facing the prospect of rising unemployment. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less